    + domainId: 1 (number, required) - The domain ID retrieved from get domains.


+ Attributes

    + `expiryDate` (string,required) - The current expiry date in any format acceptedby PHP's `DateTime` constructor, e.g. `"2026-04-01T00:00:00Z"`
     
+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                    expiryDate: "string"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            
