    + packageId: 1 (number, required) - The Package ID retrieved from get packages.
    + domainId: 1 (number, required) - The domain ID retrieved from get domains.


+ Attributes

    + `new-tag` (string,required) - The target registrar's IPS tag (e.g. `"ENOM"`)
     
+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                    new-tag: "string"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            
                true
            


